data.description: THIS IS A MUST SEE .This huge 5 bedrooms 4 1/2 bathrooms home has a great layout and room enough for everyone. There's plenty of counter space and cabinets along with a nice sized walk in pantry. There is also the flex space and the living room, along with a roomy under the stairs storage. There's also the 3 door slider that leads from the dining room to the screened in patio. Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms 3 bathrooms, a loft and the laundry room. The master suite has plenty of windows for the natural lighting with enclosed toilet room , a glass shower enclosure , a tub and his and hers sinks. The walk-in closet is big enough to house all your clothes and accessories. CLOSING WILL BE HELD AT GLOBAL TITLE PROFESSIONALS, LLC.
